{"tid":697704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「中國滾出去」 越南各地爆反中示威   反對租借土地給中國　","createTime":"2018-06-11T06:40:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T11:30:29.000Z","uid":184679,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5c439aae7c04b2fbe2c41916d3d6e4cf1bff8ea2","tid":697704,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:40:30.000Z","msg":"為了吸引外資投資，越南政府去年5月提出《經濟特區法》草案，擬在北部、中部及南部的三個省設立經濟特區，並容許外商租借土地長達99年。越南國會原定本周五（15日）表決草案。大批擔憂經濟特區被中國企業控制的民眾，周日（10日）在全國多地集會示威，首都河內至少20人遭員警帶走。<br />\n<br />\n法新社報導，越南政府擬在北部廣寧省雲屯縣（Van Don）、中部慶和省雲峰縣（Bac Van Phong），及南部堅江省富國島（Phu Quoc）設立經濟特區，透過更優惠的措施、更少的限制，來吸引外國企業投資，包括：外商的租地期限最長可達99年。草案曝光後，越南民眾深感不滿，河內、義安（Nghe An）、芽莊（Nha Trang）與胡志明市等地均爆發示威。當局出動警力，驅散人群。<br />\n <br />\n有示威者指，外國投資者在經濟特區獲得土地使用權的期限太長，可能對國家領土主權、政治、移民管理等問題產生不利影響。河內知名景點還劍湖（Hoan Kiem Lake）附近的熱鬧街道上，不少示威者更拿著反中旗幟遊行，有人高舉「土地不租給中國，一天都不行」、「No China」、「中國滾出去」，有人吶喊「反對租借土地給中國」的口號。多名示威者後來被警方押上巴士帶走。<br />\n<br />\n在民眾的反對聲音下，國會決定把周五（15日）的《經濟特區法》表決，延後至年底，以進一步徵求各界與民眾的意見。<br />\n <br />\n越南總理阮春福稱，越南經濟落後，需要透過經濟特區取得成功。而計劃與投資部部長阮志勇（Nguyen Chi Dung，音譯）澄清，經濟特區法並非要圖利中國，強調會對所有國家一視同仁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180611/1370964/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180611%2F1370964%2F&d=kPKbtd5N3Rv9bYbNO5%2FJ510Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=7d59584d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180611%2F1370964%2F&h=dfed9938\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180611/1370964/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f671297c28e2c9f6cb434cad65ba22e03c46834","tid":697704,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:43:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec97122a157bf1ab6e37d09cbacc6d14b721f70","tid":697704,"uid":70786,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:43:29.000Z","msg":"嗌口號有撚用咩<br />\n要好似印尼咁先有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e071fff82753e5a89845ecd1fa04fd352c1d69","tid":697704,"uid":72186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:55:13.000Z","msg":"排支啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"942bf19478b07e2a286d60d94871f8684dcfbc1d","tid":697704,"uid":104699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T08:26:28.000Z","msg":"姦佢老母，燒佢數簿啦"},{"pid":"e224365c215334e5ef524048ad221cee6f81ccdc","tid":697704,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T08:45:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9360ff1814f3c22ffbf07075ff6692a4d164fdd","tid":697704,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ec97122a157bf1ab6e37d09cbacc6d14b721f70","tid":697704,"uid":70786,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:43:29.000Z","msg":"嗌口號有撚用咩<br />\n要好似印尼咁先有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T08:49:23.000Z","msg":"好快就會排華 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b3b52fb9cce6694b3098520daac4adc48402e6","tid":697704,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T10:36:29.000Z","msg":"繼續租俾支那 甚至免支那稅 迫人學蝗語 設立只准支那人餐館就啱啦 迫鳩佢地排華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e420a17aa6db0796574262cb2fb35ea47bf4c77","tid":697704,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T11:14:11.000Z","msg":"越南共產黨聽民意<br />\n中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6199f49fc19f4a04aa6c2c3e31744efe8823ee81","tid":697704,"uid":44105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ec97122a157bf1ab6e37d09cbacc6d14b721f70","tid":697704,"uid":70786,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06